<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我也想像那颗流星一样，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />成为一个让大家<delay8 />
为我沉醉的偶像～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />流星啊……<delay8 />真的好浪漫！<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望有一天能找到<delay20 />可以给我讲星星的大帅哥，<delay8 />
和他一起来看流星～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光顾着看流星，<delay20 />
这次我又忘记许愿了～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那是我还小的时候吧，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />当时想要爬到彩虹上去，<delay8 />
还搞得自己迷路了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你难道不想去彩虹上走一走吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果去拜托<colour id="3" />狸克<colour id="65535" />想想办法，<delay8 />
说不定他会安排一次旅游哦～？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">之前偶然抬头望天，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正巧看到<delay8 />有一道彩虹！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉好开心呀～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然能看到两条彩虹，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这个情况可真少见！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉自己超～级幸运的，<delay8 />好开心！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />双重彩虹<delay20 />真是太少见了，<delay8 />
我拍了好多照片哦～！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要不要把它设置成屏保呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊～！<delay40 />
我还想再多看看彩虹～！<delay40 />
求你了，<delay20 />不要消失嘛～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">听说和恋人一起看极光的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能和对方<delay8 />永远在一起哦！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />听着真棒呀～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真希望有那么一天，<delay20 />能在极光下
开一场演唱会呀！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和自然的交融！<delay40 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是棒得很？！</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光帘看起来好神秘呀～<delay40 />
这种美景真的让人震撼！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大自然的力量，太了不起啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是有谁<delay8 />离开这座<tag a="110" b="32" />了吧～<delay40 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
看着渐渐消失的飞机云，<delay20 />
总有一种忧郁的感觉<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">碧蓝的画布上，<delay20 />
笔直延伸<delay8 />的白线<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay20 />这几句<delay8 />好像可以作歌词！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">听说<delay8 />看到飞机云之后，
去和喜欢的人告白就会成功，<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说不定我今天<delay8 />会被谁告白哦～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">充分沐浴了月光之后，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就要拥有<delay8 />足够的满月能量啦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">月亮上不是有图案的吗？<delay20 />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看起来就像穿着一身裙子的我呀～<delay40 />
<anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难不成，<delay20 />我可能是月亮公主？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一看到满月，<delay20 />感觉全身都充满了力量呀！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过肚子并没有一起充满，<delay8 />
所以我有点想吃团子～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>